{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 8,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 416.215,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.043,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then we had gathered together",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 2.223,
      "end": 6.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all manner of seeds of every kind, both of grain of every kind,",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 6.49,
      "end": 9.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of the seeds of fruit of every kind.",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 10.142,
      "end": 12.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then while my father stayed in the wilderness",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 13.155,
      "end": 14.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spoke to us, saying:",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 14.96,
      "end": 17.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I have dreamed a dream;",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.23,
      "end": 20.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in other words, I have seen a vision.",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.696,
      "end": 24.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, because of the thing which I have seen,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 24.452,
      "end": 26.867,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have reason to rejoice in the Lord,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 27.047,
      "end": 29.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of Nephi and also of Sam;",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 29.874,
      "end": 31.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have reason to suppose",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 32.051,
      "end": 33.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 33.346,
      "end": 35.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many of their seed,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 35.662,
      "end": 36.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be saved.",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 37.642,
      "end": 39.778,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, Laman and Lemuel,",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 39.958,
      "end": 42.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I fear greatly because of you;",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 42.321,
      "end": 44.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, I thought I saw in my dream,",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 45.009,
      "end": 47.424,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a dark and dreary wilderness.",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 48.104,
      "end": 49.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw a man,",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 49.863,
      "end": 51.906,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he was dressed in a white robe;",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 52.086,
      "end": 53.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he came and stood before me.",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 54.577,
      "end": 56.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then he spoke to me,",
      "verse": "8:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 56.382,
      "end": 57.915,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and told me follow him.",
      "verse": "8:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 58.595,
      "end": 60.267,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then as I followed him",
      "verse": "8:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 60.447,
      "end": 64.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw myself that I was in a dark and dreary waste.",
      "verse": "8:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 64.842,
      "end": 69.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I had traveled for the space of many hours in darkness,",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 69.387,
      "end": 71.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to pray to the Lord",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 71.471,
      "end": 73.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would have mercy on me,",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 73.462,
      "end": 77.084,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the multitude of his tender mercies.",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 77.764,
      "end": 80.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had prayed to the Lord",
      "verse": "8:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 80.312,
      "end": 82.634,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw a large and spacious field.",
      "verse": "8:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 83.314,
      "end": 84.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw a tree,",
      "verse": "8:10",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 85.119,
      "end": 87.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose fruit was desirable to make one happy.",
      "verse": "8:10",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 88.585,
      "end": 90.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I went forth",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 90.251,
      "end": 92.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit of it;",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 92.567,
      "end": 94.889,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw that it was most sweet,",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 95.069,
      "end": 97.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "above all that I ever before tasted.",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 97.85,
      "end": 101.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, and I saw that the fruit of it was white,",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 101.281,
      "end": 104.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to exceed all the whiteness that I had ever seen.",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 105.537,
      "end": 108.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as I partook of the fruit of it",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 108.364,
      "end": 110.686,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it filled my soul with very great joy;",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 110.866,
      "end": 112.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I began to be desirous",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 113.089,
      "end": 115.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my family should partake of it also;",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 115.963,
      "end": 119.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I knew that it was desirable above all other fruit.",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 120.172,
      "end": 122.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as I cast my eyes round about,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 122.581,
      "end": 125.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps I might discover my family also,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 125.64,
      "end": 127.498,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw a river of water;",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 127.678,
      "end": 129.164,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it ran along,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 129.344,
      "end": 130.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was near the tree",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 131.103,
      "end": 133.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I was partaking the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 134.151,
      "end": 136.659,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked to behold from where it came;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 136.839,
      "end": 139.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the head of it a little way off;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 139.666,
      "end": 142.499,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and at the head of it I saw your mother Sariah,",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 142.679,
      "end": 144.444,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Sam, and Nephi;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 144.624,
      "end": 147.457,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they stood as if they knew not where they should go.",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 148.137,
      "end": 150.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I beckoned to them;",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 150.267,
      "end": 152.914,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I also said to them with a loud voice",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 153.094,
      "end": 154.673,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they should come to me,",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 154.853,
      "end": 156.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit,",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 156.751,
      "end": 159.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was desirable above all other fruit.",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 160.217,
      "end": 161.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they came to me",
      "verse": "8:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 161.93,
      "end": 164.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit also.",
      "verse": "8:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 164.886,
      "end": 168.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I was desirous that Laman and Lemuel should come",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 168.735,
      "end": 170.918,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit also;",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 171.098,
      "end": 172.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I cast my eyes",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 172.718,
      "end": 175.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards the head of the river,",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 175.22,
      "end": 177.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps I might see them.",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 178.361,
      "end": 180.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw them,",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 180.259,
      "end": 181.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but they would not come to me",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 182.157,
      "end": 183.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 184.416,
      "end": 186.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw a rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 186.407,
      "end": 189.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it extended along the bank of the river,",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 189.234,
      "end": 191.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and led to the tree by which I stood.",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 192.468,
      "end": 195.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw a strait and narrow path,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 195.434,
      "end": 197.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which came along by the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 198.168,
      "end": 200.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even to the tree by which I stood;",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 200.577,
      "end": 203.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it also led by the head of the fountain,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 203.961,
      "end": 207.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to a large and spacious field, as if it had been a world.",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 208.356,
      "end": 210.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw numberless crowds of people,",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 210.997,
      "end": 213.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of whom were pressing forward,",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 213.453,
      "end": 216.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might obtain the path",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 216.512,
      "end": 218.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which led to the tree by which I stood.",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 219.468,
      "end": 221.186,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then they came forth,",
      "verse": "8:22",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 221.366,
      "end": 224.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and commence in the path which led to the tree.",
      "verse": "8:22",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 225.018,
      "end": 228.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then there arose a mist of darkness;",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 228.217,
      "end": 231.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even a very great mist of darkness,",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 231.834,
      "end": 236.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so much so that they who had begun in the path lost their way,",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 236.286,
      "end": 238.794,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they wandered off and were lost.",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 239.474,
      "end": 241.842,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw others pressing forward,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 242.022,
      "end": 246.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they came forth and caught hold of the end of the rod of iron;",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 246.567,
      "end": 250.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they pressed forward through the mist of darkness,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 250.323,
      "end": 252.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "clinging to the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 252.453,
      "end": 254.311,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even until they came forth",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 254.491,
      "end": 256.627,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit of the tree.",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 257.307,
      "end": 260.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had partaken of the fruit of the tree",
      "verse": "8:25",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 260.413,
      "end": 263.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they cast their eyes about as if they were ashamed.",
      "verse": "8:25",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 264.112,
      "end": 266.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also cast my eyes round about,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 266.8,
      "end": 270.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw, on the other side of the river of water,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 270.835,
      "end": 273.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a great and spacious building;",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 273.198,
      "end": 275.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it stood as it were in the air,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 275.421,
      "end": 277.139,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "high above the earth.",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 277.819,
      "end": 279.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it was filled with people,",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 279.717,
      "end": 281.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both old and young,",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 281.662,
      "end": 283.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both male and female;",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 283.56,
      "end": 286.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their manner of dress was very fine;",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 286.434,
      "end": 289.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were in the attitude of mocking and pointing their fingers",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 290.143,
      "end": 294.044,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards those who had come at and were partaking of the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 294.724,
      "end": 297.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had tasted of the fruit they were ashamed,",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 298.015,
      "end": 300.523,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of those that were scoffing at them;",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 300.703,
      "end": 304.279,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they fell away into forbidden paths and were lost.",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 304.959,
      "end": 308.721,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not speak all the words of my father.",
      "verse": "8:29",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 309.401,
      "end": 311.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, to be short in writing,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 311.671,
      "end": 315.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he saw other multitudes pressing forward;",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 315.241,
      "end": 318.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they came and caught hold of the end of the rod of iron;",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 319.043,
      "end": 321.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they pressed their way forward,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 321.22,
      "end": 324.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "continually holding fast to the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 324.419,
      "end": 326.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until they came forth and fell down",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 326.782,
      "end": 329.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partook of the fruit of the tree.",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 329.923,
      "end": 332.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also saw other multitudes",
      "verse": "8:31",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 332.286,
      "end": 335.908,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeling their way towards that great and spacious building.",
      "verse": "8:31",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 336.588,
      "end": 340.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then many were drowned in the depths of the fountain;",
      "verse": "8:32",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 340.205,
      "end": 344.06,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many were lost from his view, wandering in strange roads.",
      "verse": "8:32",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 344.74,
      "end": 346.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And great was the multitude",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 346.731,
      "end": 349.378,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that entered into that strange building.",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 349.558,
      "end": 352.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they entered into that building",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 352.478,
      "end": 355.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they pointed the finger of scorn at me",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 355.212,
      "end": 358.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those that were partaking of the fruit also;",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 358.318,
      "end": 359.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but we heeded them not.",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 360.531,
      "end": 362.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are the words of my father:",
      "verse": "8:34",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 362.661,
      "end": 365.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For as many as heeded them, had fallen away.",
      "verse": "8:34",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 366.452,
      "end": 370.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Laman and Lemuel partook not of the fruit, said my father.",
      "verse": "8:35",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 371.079,
      "end": 373.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after my father had spoken",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 373.72,
      "end": 375.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all the words of his dream or vision,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 376.176,
      "end": 377.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were many,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 377.889,
      "end": 381.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he said to us, because of these things which he saw in a vision,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 381.645,
      "end": 384.013,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he very feared for Laman and Lemuel;",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 384.193,
      "end": 389.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, he feared for fear that they should be cast off from the presence of the Lord.",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 389.703,
      "end": 391.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he urged them then",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 391.648,
      "end": 394.156,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with all the feeling of a tender parent,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 394.336,
      "end": 396.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would listen to his words,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 396.838,
      "end": 399.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps the Lord would be merciful to them,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 399.944,
      "end": 401.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not cast them off;",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 401.61,
      "end": 404.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, my father preached to them.",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 404.705,
      "end": 407.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had preached to them,",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 407.253,
      "end": 410.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also prophesied to them of many things,",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 410.452,
      "end": 413.331,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he told them to keep the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 413.511,
      "end": 415.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he ceased speaking to them.",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 151
    }
  ]
}